HEADWORD: Fractionally
<hw>Frac"tion*al*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>By fractions or separate
portions; <as>as, to distill a liquid <ex>fractionally</ex>, that is, so
as to separate different portions</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
